headline: Benson Hill, Inc. (BHIL) Reports Q3 Loss, Misses Revenue Estimates
summary: Star Peak Corp II (BHIL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -27.01% and 12.79%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
